{
  "texts": [
    "Thus, H2, H3 and H4 was supported while H5 was not supported.",
    "PUàBI (β = 0.100, p< 0.01) and ATTàBI (β = 0.964, p< 0.01) were positively related to Intention thus supporting H1 and H6 of this study.",
    "Finally, we tested the mediation analysis following the Preacher and Hayes (2004) method by bootstrapping the indirect effect.",
    "PUàATTàBI (β = 0.118, p< 0.01) was significant with no 0 straddling the lower and upper limit thus confirming H7.",
    "This study examined how students' acceptance and use of ChatGPT, a recently developed AI-based technology, affected their TAM-based education."
